          "reviewBody": "School infrastructure good.Slogams,safety, cultural,prayers for traditional events good.They will teach every kid and make them above average.\nBut not enough encouragement in sports.though they ve space,they are not willing to coach sports.and also extra curricular activities.they don't let children to participate in dance or skit consecutive years.once in a four years only participation.\nAnd for higher secondary education,they lack to prepare for competitive exams since all competitive exams are CBSE oriented, we opting for CBSE schools.",
