            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "1. Dont see the reviews\n2. Private schools are running profit earning business. So teachers quality is concerns everywhere.\n3. Well knowledged and proper trained teachers are so expensive to hire. So you have to understand the outcomes.\n4. Instead of teaching your ward, most of the school management will take lessons to parents\n5. Schools are meant to enlighten the students, but all schools conducting entrance exam for selection which is so contradict\n6. Dont care about front office executive. If school fee is high (1.2 lac and above), you get good response. if not, ....\n7. Factors to choose the right one;\na. Distance from your home\nb. Availability of school transport\nc. Avoid private transport\nd. Fee structure\ne. Get to know about the school from existing students & their parents\nf. Children's count in class sections (less than 30 is better)",
          "publisher": {
